In [2]:
epoch = 1000

epsilon0 = 0.9

print(mapfile, destfile, trapfile)
for alpha1 in [0.1*i for i in range(1,10)]:
    for gamma in [0.1*i for i in range(4,10)]:
        print('alpha:{} gamma:{}'.format(alpha1, gamma))

        g1 = Maze.Maze(from_file=mapfile)
        g1.set_dest_and_traps(dest_file=destfile, traps_file=trapfile)
        r1 = Robot.Robot(g1,alpha=alpha1, epsilon0=epsilon0, gamma=gamma)
        r1.set_status(learning=True)

        runner1 = Runner.Runner(r1, g1)
        runner1.run_training(epoch, training_per_epoch=1000, display_direction=True)
        runner1.plot_results(save_file=None)
